{{version030}}
{{Flavour|Instills a corruption within all visible targets, temporarily mutating their bodies in an adverse fashion. It cannot affect artificial beings, and the undead will decompose if affected.}}

'''Corrupting Pulse''' is a spell that inflicts 1-2 transient (temporary) [[mutation]]s to targets in [[line of sight]]. There is a 25% chance to inflict 2 mutations, otherwise you receive 1.<ref>{{source ref|0.30.0|mon-cast.cc|3227}}</ref> These mutations can be cured by gaining [[XP]].

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*In [[0.29]], this ability can inflict multiple transient mutations again.
*In [[0.28]], this ability could only inflict up to 1 transient mutation.

